message:
HI ALL!!!  WOW prices go up TOMORROW (crazy how last week I said it goes up in a week, and here we are, a week later... and here they are, a week later, going up...). With that said!! I challenge you all to take that step/leap/waddle/flounder/sprint/jump/etc. in signing up for CWC!  I will personally be really happy for each individual person who signs up, and if you're trying to make me happy today, that would be the way to do it.  

http://www.twincitiescru.com/opportunities/winter-conference/

Good luck with finals and to all a good night!!!!
